Project Structure
-----------------

    memory/
    ├── main.cpp      - Entry point and game initialization
    ├── memory.cpp    - Main game logic and rendering
    ├── memory.hpp    - Header file with game structures
    ├── Makefile      - Build configuration
    └── README.txt    - This file


Troubleshooting
---------------

Game doesn't display properly?
    - Make sure your terminal supports at least 80x24 characters
    - Full-screen your terminal window for best experience
    - Some terminals may need to be resized after launching

Colors not showing?
    - Ensure your terminal supports colors (echo $TERM)
    - Try setting: export TERM=xterm-256color

Compilation errors?
    - Verify ncurses is installed correctly
    - Check that you're using C++17 or later
    - Run make clean then make again


